 &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13302,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/04\/05\/salat-nisa-hijab-wajib\/","url_meta":{"origin":28905,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Hijab: Adult women must pray wearing veils","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 5, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe prayer of a menstruating woman is not accepted unless she wears a veil,\u201d by which he meant an adult woman. Imam al-Tirmidhi said, \"This is acted upon by the people of knowledge, that when a woman prays and\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31757,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/03\/no-salat-asr-fajr-exceptions\/","url_meta":{"origin":28905,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Salat: No voluntary prayer after \u2018Asr and Fajr, with exceptions","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 3, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, only prayed two cycles after the afternoon prayer because some property came to him, which occupied him from performing two cycles after the noon prayer. The Prophet prayed them after the afternoon prayer and he did not repeat it.\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31728,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/02\/imam-turn-around-after-salat\/","url_meta":{"origin":28905,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Imam should turn around after finishing prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 2, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Yazid ibn al-Aswad reported: I prayed behind the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, and when he finished, he would turn around to face us. Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 614 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u064a\u064e\u0632\u0650\u064a\u062f\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0623\u064e\u0633\u0652\u0648\u064e\u062f\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062a\u064f \u062e\u064e\u0644\u0652\u0641\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25718,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/01\/09\/salat-jamaah-already-prayed\/","url_meta":{"origin":28905,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Jama&#8217;ah: Pray with congregation, even if already prayed","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 9, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Yazid ibn Al-Aswad reported: I witness the Hajj pilgrimage with the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and I prayed the dawn prayer with him in the mosque of Al-Khaif. When the Prophet finished his prayer and turned around, he saw two men in